On Tue, 15 Aug 2006, Bill Price wrote:
> What would cause the brake warning light to flash opposite the turn signals
> when I put the turn signals on?

Bad ground.  Go to the back and wiggle the connections on the tail lights.
That fixed mine when it did the same thing.

Might also be the grounds on the front signals, of course.

George
